ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of M.H. (MIKE) SHAIKH, of Calgary, Alberta, as a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Anil Wirasekara.
